claim.claim-text:
A digital signal recording apparatus (DR) for recording digital data (Sa and Sv) comprised of a plurality of recording blocks (Br) on a recording medium, said apparatus comprising:

   a grouping means (5) for making a group of said digital data (Sa and Sv) according to a predetermined time-based interval (St);

   a data block generating means (4) for dividing said input data (Sa and Sv) included in each of said sequence into a plurality of data blocks (Db);

   a sequence number generating means (6) for dividing said group into "N" sequences, said "N" being an integer, to generate a sequence number (Ss) for each of said data blocks (Db) associated with each of said recording blocks (Br);

   an ID block generating means (23 and 24) for generating an ID information of each of said data block (Br) based on said sequence number (Ss); and

   a recording block generating means (8 and 9) for generating said recording block (Br) based on said ID information and said data block (Db; Sa and Sv).

A digital signal recording apparatus (DR) for recording digital data (Sr; Sa and Sv) comprised of a plurality of recording blocks (Br), each of said recording blocks (Br) having an ID block (ID) including "N" divided sequence number (Ss') thereof and data block (Db'; Sa and Sv), said apparatus comprising:

   a data block extracting means (12a) for extracting said data block (Db) from said digital data (Sa and Sv);

   a sequence number extracting means (12b) for extracting said sequence number (Ss') from said digital data (Sr; Sa and Sv);

   an ID block generating means (23 and 24) for producing an ID information (ID) for said extracted data block (Db') based on said extracted sequence number (Ss'); and

   a recording block generating means (8 and 9) for generating a recording block (Br) based on said ID information (ID) and said extracted data block (Db'; Sa and Sv).
